---
title: American BBQ Tofu & Cheesy Charred Corn Bowl with Garlic Rice & Plant-Based Mayo
description: We’re cooking up tonight’s little tofu cubes in a lavish dark sauce. Smokey-sweet BBQ sauce and hot sriracha come together for a flavourful marinade that packs a punch. Pull it together with garlic rice and charred corn, plus a dollop of creamy mayo for a taste of decadence in a bowl!

